eNCA's Rofhiwa Madzena speaks ANC spokesperson Pule Mabe. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The ANC National Executive Committee is meeting on Sunday, to process policy discussion documents.
This is in preparation for the party's national policy conference later in the year.For more on this, eNCA's Rofhiwa Madzena speaks ANC spokesperson Pule Mabe.